  %p#main
    Pastor J.S Ajulo has been a consistent preacher and teacher of the word of God for the past 40 years. A Pharmacy graduate of the University of Ife, now Obafemi Awolowo University, and Master Degree holder from the West Africa Theological Seminary (affiliated to the University of Nigeria, Nsuka.) He has been used by God to spread the gospel, not only in Africa, but also across the world. As an experienced Minister of the Gospel and a pioneer in several moves of the Holy Spirit, he has become a father and mentor to many Christians today. An anointed minister, scholar and Bible teacher, he has a passion to see Christians live in constant victory in their spiritual lives and all other aspects of their existence, and ministers healing and deliverance to the body of Christ. He is the General Overseer of the Bible Believers Church Ministries whose headquarters is in Lagos Nigeria. Pastor Ajulo is a father of three children.
